Course provides knowledge and skills of teaching methods in chosen sport speciality field. The course gives overview of teaching physical abilities and physical training to conduct effective training process. Composing training plans in chosen sport speciality field are examined.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Basic knowledge and skills of teaching methods in chosen sport speciality field. The course provide fundamental knowledge of teaching sports and conducting effective training process.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After course student: 1) has knowledge and practical skills of teaching  physical abilities in chosen sport speciality field; 2) has knowledge and practical skills of teaching general and specific physical training in chosen sport speciality field; 3) has knowledge and practical skills of conducting effective process of training in chosen sport speciality field; 4) is capable to compose training plans in annual and perennial training process of chosen sport speciality field.
